comments: Tucker (PHI) moves alongside Brunson's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact initiated by Brunson.
Harris (PHI) and Barrett (NYK) mutually engage, as they are disengaging Harris slightly extends his arm into Barrett.
Brunson (NYK) reaches in and delivers contact to Harrell's (PHI) arm.
Randle (NYK) establishes a screening position and does not deliver illegal contact to Harris (PHI) as Harris is moving through the pick.,
Randle (NYK) establishes his right foot as his pivot and passes the ball before his pivot foot returns to the floor.
Reed (PHI) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Harris (PHI) brings his off-arm toward Barrett's (NYK) side and marginal contact occurs as Harris (PHI) attempts to move around Barrett (NYK) off-ball in the post.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Maxey (PHI) passes the ball out of bounds.
Reed (PHI) does not maintain a legal vertical position while contesting Brunson's (NYK) shot attempt and initiates contact as he turns his body.
Reddish (NYK) gets beat to the spot and delivers contact to Harris' (PHI) arm during his shot attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) gets beat to the spot and delivers contact to Barrett (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) extends his arms into Tucker (PHI) and dislodges him from his screening position.
Tucker (PHI) clamps and holds Randle's (NYK) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Toppin (NYK) gets beat to the spot and initiates contact to Maxey (PHI) during his driving shot attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) commits a take foul against Randle (NYK).
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul against Brunson (NYK).
Randle (NYK) and Tucker (PHI) engage and then disengage during the made free throw.
Maxey (PHI) and Quickley (NYK) mutually engage, as they are disengaging, Maxey slightly extends his arm into Quickley.
Randle (NYK) gets to ball height and cleanly dislodges the ball from Tucker (PHI), any ensuing contact is incidental.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Tucker (PHI) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to the Knicks.
